msgid "# Remove-WorkgroupClusterNode"
msgstr "# 删除工作组集群节点"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Removes a node from a workgroup cluster."
msgstr "从工作组集群中删除一个节点。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The `Remove-WorkgroupCluster` function removes a node from the membership in a workgroup Cluster.\n"
"The rest of the parameters will be forwarded to the `Remove-ClusterNode` function. Please refer to\n"
"the documentation for the\n"
"[Remove-ClusterNode](/powershell/module/failoverclusters/remove-clusternode) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"`Remove-WorkgroupCluster` 函数用于将某个节点从工作组集群（workgroup "
"cluster）的成员列表中移除。其余参数将会被传递给 `Remove-ClusterNode` 函数。有关 [Remove-"
"ClusterNode](/powershell/module/failoverclusters/remove-clusternode) cmdlet "
"的详细信息，请参阅相关文档。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### EXAMPLE 1"
msgstr "### 示例 1"

msgid "This example removes `Node2` from the cluster membership."
msgstr "这个示例将 `Node2` 从集群成员列表中删除。"

msgid "### EXAMPLE 2"
msgstr "### 示例 2"

msgid "This example removes `Node3` from the cluster membership."
msgstr "这个示例会将 `Node3` 从集群成员中移除。"

msgid ""
"Manual cleanup may be required to clear the node state by logging into `Node3` and running\n"
"`Clear-ClusterNode`."
msgstr "可能需要手动进行清理操作，才能通过登录到 `Node3` 并运行 `Clear-ClusterNode` 命令来恢复节点的正常状态。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "An array of nodes in the workgroup cluster."
msgstr "工作组集群中的一系列节点。"

msgid "An array of credentials for the nodes."
msgstr "用于这些节点的一组凭据信息。"

msgid ""
"The name of the node to be removed. If the name isn't included in **Node** parameter, the first\n"
"node in the **Node** parameter will be used to remove the node. Additional cleanup will be required\n"
"to clear the node state."
msgstr ""
"需要删除的节点的名称。如果该名称没有包含在 `Node` 参数中，那么将使用 `Node` "
"参数中的第一个节点来执行删除操作。此外，还需要进行额外的清理工作以清除该节点的状态信息。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the time in seconds to wait for the cmdlet. If the **Wait** parameter isn't specified,\n"
"then the cmdlet waits for completion. If the value `0` is specified, then the call is initiated and\n"
"the cmdlet returns without waiting."
msgstr ""
"指定等待该cmdlet完成所需的时间（以秒为单位）。如果未指定**Wait**参数，那么cmdlet会一直等待直到任务完成。如果指定值为`0`，则命令会被立即执行，cmdlet会在不等待的情况下立即返回结果。"

msgid ""
"Removes any residual cluster metadata from the specified disks. This metadata includes information\n"
"that the cluster service uses to manage the disks. By cleaning the metadata, the disks are freed\n"
"from any old cluster configurations, making them available for new clusters or other purposes. This\n"
"cmdlet may prevent potential conflicts that could arise from leftover metadata when reusing disks."
msgstr ""
"从指定的磁盘上删除所有残留的集群元数据。这些元数据包含集群服务用于管理磁盘的信息。通过清除元数据，磁盘就可以摆脱旧的集群配置，从而可以将其用于新的集群或其他用途。此cmdlet可以避免在重新使用磁盘时由于残留元数据而可能引发的潜在冲突。"

msgid "Forces the command to run without asking for user confirmation."
msgstr "强制命令运行，而不会询问用户的确认。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that this cmdlet doesn't check whether the cluster node contains non-shared storage, if\n"
"Storage Spaces Direct is enabled. If you don't specify this parameter, the cmdlet checks whether\n"
"this node has any Storage Spaces Direct storage. If this cmdlet finds Storage Spaces Direct storage,\n"
"it prompts you for confirmation before it removes the node."
msgstr ""
"该参数表示：即使启用了“Storage Spaces "
"Direct”功能，此cmdlet也不会检查集群节点是否包含非共享存储资源。如果您未指定此参数，cmdlet会自动检查该节点是否存在“Storage "
"Spaces Direct”存储资源。如果发现存在此类存储资源，在删除该节点之前，系统会提示您进行确认。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行cmdlet之前，会提示您进行确认。"

msgid "Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs. The cmdlet isn't run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行该cmdlet。"

